{"tid":1203173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警護航，APM黑力架屈人偷野","createTime":"2019-06-11T11:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T12:50:11.000Z","uid":233873,"like":90,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0a8fc8b2597cedff459dc259eedf13f631046969","tid":1203173,"uid":233873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7MoQ9qB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7MoQ9qB.png&h=e7e9e90e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說我朋友今日係APM Unique 買衫，之後搭電梯走個陣，突然有個黑力架同佢講蝗語，問我朋友<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「你懂不懂普通話？」</span></span>我朋友仲諗住佢想問路，諗住幫佢。<br />\n<br />\n點知，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個黑力架講：「I am not a thief，但是我看到你做了什麼，別再讓我看見你們。」</span></span>講完就搭對面電梯上番去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我朋友get到黑力架話佢偷野之後，當然把鬼火屌佢痴撚線。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後個黑力架唔撚服氣，就追番落去理論。「在我國家，是不會有人偷東西的。」鬧我朋友係bitch。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好快APM職員就到左，問發生咩事，有一個職員睇左張unique 收據之後，就即刻<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">屌柒條黑力架，叫佢收聲。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後個黑力架要求報警，我朋友亦話好，就報警。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過左差唔多20分鐘，警察尼左了解情況，警察竟然話條黑力架無講過我朋友偷野，而係話佢種族歧視佢，侮辱佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個黑力架仲要求我朋友道歉，同埋del左影佢張相。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個位朋友趕住要買物資，就同條黑力互相道歉。個黑力架走左之後，<span style=\"color: red;\">班黑警仲懶係野咁講：「洗唔洗安慰下你？」</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我同佢iCloud 就相連既，見到張相既時候我亦Save低左。在此奉上圖一張。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個朋友講，班黑警唔理佢既口供，不斷叫佢道歉，話無證據能證明黑力架屈佢偷野，只能民事訴訟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但朋友叫班黑警check CCTV既時候就唔理佢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽聞此人係APM 25樓返工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如見此人，請謹慎行事，比人屈偷野就唔好啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申：以上絕無歧視成份，黑力架為「黑人力量十分架勢」既簡稱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBetween，see you tmr 朝早一齊去野餐，學學黑力架，有健康既體魄。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a61fceafff0bc3017e2847d5000a6df76928b1","tid":1203173,"uid":62646,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:48:59.000Z","msg":"死力架"},{"pid":"a85aae5455329113603b976aa2a3a4d673f6d5c4","tid":1203173,"uid":44718,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:50:29.000Z","msg":"Niggative"},{"pid":"0e070464ac090ae40c8e094dc8eb43f46623e3df","tid":1203173,"uid":76999,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:51:13.000Z","msg":"唔偷  全部都係搶或者姦殺炸嘛"},{"pid":"824b88d989eaf508c1762fda36e0605eff517f86","tid":1203173,"uid":99700,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:52:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u5kgkTF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu5kgkTF.png&h=95dd50f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0f547c417e5fb1a0f74f529ac2931714ff0b9e5","tid":1203173,"uid":218699,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:52:23.000Z","msg":"力架國家窮到冇野可偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c87b7ef8a7bba3ff2f9cdc96002c422afc6b3293","tid":1203173,"uid":10023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:53:38.000Z","msg":"黑人力量十分架勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44fc237d7d65b5490c479d14676c8533c955d541","tid":1203173,"uid":144064,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/lhJMCV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FlhJMCV4.jpg&h=d33685bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5df999b3fbd34724d060895beb1a6306d3165ff7","tid":1203173,"uid":53505,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:57:03.000Z","msg":"有冇係佢面前鬧佢力架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf0de60a8a4aad8bd516cd13db43f97648b0999","tid":1203173,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:59:02.000Z","msg":"同佢講 香港差佬is a big friend of 美國差佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢就明"},{"pid":"ad0729caef5700deaae51e44f5d1d808c91f71f8","tid":1203173,"uid":194994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:02:15.000Z","msg":"Nigga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111b6f49787a10965f6f5a6ccabe391e638718f0","tid":1203173,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:05:15.000Z","msg":"黑克都算 <br />\n警察最仆街"},{"pid":"460eb3e401b611f9f819d28065f05d52d4bd3b95","tid":1203173,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:08:51.000Z","msg":"香港玩racism行唔通架喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc62d3f4759e2e1e029f0b05386dc3f24112e55","tid":1203173,"uid":213142,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:11:25.000Z","msg":"道咩歉，應該唔好道歉<br />\n夠薑叫嘉頓向佢道歉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cuUEiML.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcuUEiML.png&h=009e5d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ff997f47af4d8068018446378903465243c4368","tid":1203173,"uid":91644,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.4pcdn.org/pol/1549738353896.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.4pcdn.org%2Fpol%2F1549738353896.jpg&h=ba1b6d7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b38aca3741cb283b6fa0bbadc079c525de69607","tid":1203173,"uid":28913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:48:49.000Z","msg":"黑警梗係幫力架, 大家都係賊黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1e2e3f77caa400e1b97ad5f1663c2281c4a688","tid":1203173,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hy26Jrm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai